dct_title_s: Bosnia and Herzegovina city graphic 1:15,000. Brcko. Series M903
dct_description_sm: United States. Defense Mapping Agency. Alternate title: Brcko.Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 5 meter contour intervals, and spot elevations. Coordinate conversion WGS 84 to ED 50. "Map information as of 1994."This sheet falls within NL34-10, 1501, 1:250,000 and 2884 IV, M709, 1:50,000. Reprinted by NIMA 3-01. "This map is red light readable.".
